title: Marvel's Ultimate Universe
description:
Not much to say here. This is EVERY issue from Marvel's Ultimate Universe from over the years.

These books are arranged in the order they should be read. 669 issues over 668 cbr/cbz files. (Wolverine Vs. Hulk 1 & 2 are a single Director's Cut because it was higher quality.)

This way you can skip whatever issues that don't interest you without feeling like you're missing any of the "total story".

Please note that I did not create any of these files. I've just accumulated and organized a bunch of other torrents into a single easy to follow comic book experience.

Enjoy!
